==English==

===Noun===
'''fungus''' (''plural:'' '''fungi''' ''or'' '''funguses''')

#a category of [[eukaryote|eukaryotic]] organism, having [[cell wall]]s but no [[chlorophyll]]. Fungi may be unicellular or multicellular.

